                    <p>The Duck Brilliance Pipeline is a flexible, production-ready data processing framework designed for data scientists, ML engineers, and data engineers. It provides a clean, modular architecture for building reproducible data transformation pipelines.</p>
                    
                    <div class="quick-start">
                        <h2><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i> Quick Start</h2>
                        <pre><code># Install
pip install duck-brilliance-pipeline

# Run with config
duck-brilliance-pipeline -c config.yaml

# Or use in Python
from pipeline.main import DataPipeline
pipeline = DataPipeline("config.yaml").run()</code></pre>
                    </div>
                    
